    <h1>Winter Closure</h1>
    <p><strong>The Museum is closed for the winter season. </strong></p>
    <p>Access is available by appointment for group tours, education programs and researchers. Call 250-992-9580 or <a href="mailto:ehunter@quesnel.ca">click here</a> to make arrangements.<br>
    </p>
    <p><strong>The Museum will be open on December 4 &amp; 5, 2015, 9:30 a.m. - 4 p.m. for our <a href="GiftShopandActivities.html">Annual Christmas Sale</a></strong></p>
    <p>&nbsp;</p>
    <h1><strong>2016 Season</strong></h1>
